    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> → do we want to avoid it?\r\n\r\nThat's not easy to answer. It'll add overhead to both our code and the middleware usage with conditional requirements. We have the same problem with the widget definition where nothing is required, but you still have to provide either `init` or `render`. You can't type-check that. That's why I don't think that this PR is necessary personally.",
